475
00:20:50,750 --> 00:20:51,650
hendak bermula?

476
00:20:52,270 --> 00:20:53,830
Adakah anda semua bersedia?

477
00:20:54,640 --> 00:20:56,170
Hanya memberi perintah,

478
00:20:57,590 --> 00:20:59,790
dan kami akan memberikan nyawa kami
tanpa teragak-agak.

479
00:20:59,790 --> 00:21:01,030
Bagaimana jika saya memerintahkan anda

480
00:21:02,110 --> 00:21:03,970
untuk membunuh Maharaja, Xia Jingyan?

481
00:21:08,550 --> 00:21:09,110
